&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Escalation and Support&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the escalation point for complex issues unresolved by the internal helpdesk team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an escalation point for backup remediation, ensuring critical data recovery and system integrity.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Onboarding and Offboarding&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee internal user onboarding and offboarding processes to ensure a seamless experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage client onboarding and offboarding, ensuring all systems, accounts, and configurations are properly set up or decommissioned.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure Architecture and Maintenance&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, maintain, and troubleshoot datacenter and cloud infrastructure, focusing on Windows and Azure environments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain backup infrastructure architecture using Veeam to ensure reliable data protection and recovery.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backup Management&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, deploy, and maintain Veeam backup solutions for internal and client environments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform regular backup verification with Veeam to ensure integrity and recoverability of data.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate and remediate backup failures, ensuring minimal downtime and data loss.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize Veeam backup policies and strategies for efficiency, compliance, and security.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RMM (Remote Monitoring and Management)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
